::KitKat::

She looked at Drillbit. "Not for a little while yet. I"m still in the 
planning stages." she looked down."But it may never get that far 
even. Terrorsaur hated the idea and I'm afraid he'll tell Megatron." 
she sighed. "Maybe he's right. It was a pathetic idea." She walked 
passed Drillbit and out of her room. She turned down the hallway and 
went to the mess hall.  She went over to the bar, poured herself an 
energin and sat down at a table.  She didn't even take a sip of her 
drink.  She just sat there looking at the glass.
